  <brief_title>Local Infiltration Analgesia in Total Knee Arthroplasty</brief_title>
  <official_title>Local Infiltration Analgesia in Total Knee Arthroplasty: A Randomized, Prospective, Placebo Controlled, Double Blinded Study.</official_title>
